{"tid":943190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國警方例行搜身 竟揉掐少女胸部","createTime":"2018-12-16T11:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T13:11:01.000Z","uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"59c04adfa63f9892349eb1afc1647392da133d0d","tid":943190,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:03:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-tw/news/world/中國警方例行搜身-竟揉掐少女胸部/ar-BBQZ347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E4%BE%8B%E8%A1%8C%E6%90%9C%E8%BA%AB-%E7%AB%9F%E6%8F%89%E6%8E%90%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%83%B8%E9%83%A8%2Far-BBQZ347&d=fJ0fjb7amM2REB7KPccfti7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=dd4731e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.msn.com/zh-tw/news/world/中國警方例行搜身-竟揉掐少女胸部/ar-BBQZ347</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n先前有傳聞，中國在新疆一帶以「打擊恐怖主義」為名，背後卻是在迫害維吾爾族，許多族人在一般場合都會受到警察多次臨檢。近日網路上流傳一段影片，只見一名中國男警，正在對公車上的女乘客搜身，沒想到他卻當眾摸、掐女乘客的胸部。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOizXWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOizXWC.jpg&h=a1619522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&copy; 由 Sanlih E-television Co., LTD 提供 中國新疆特警搜身，竟揉捏年輕女「胸器」。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n▲中國警方伸手掐住女子胸部。（圖／翻攝自YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，中國當局下令，要求新疆警方特別在公共場合對民眾進行身分驗證，並還要全面搜身。現在卻流出一段影片，疑似是新疆警方正在對剛下公車的民眾進行搜身，只見一名男警先是身手摸了女乘客的胸部，接著掐了幾下，最後才摸向女乘客的腹部。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QsIv8sJ0UeU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQsIv8sJ0UeU&d=fJ0fjb7amM2REB7KPccfti7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c32de285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QsIv8sJ0UeU</a><br />\n<br />\n整段影片中，可以發現女乘客的表情相當漠然，這也讓網友氣得說「厲害了，你的國」、「見光的都這樣了，沒見光的更不用說 」、「實在太惡劣了」、「男警可以這樣摸女生」、「光看就想吐了」。"},{"pid":"393315f14469e755106fa767f03fb27255df2078","tid":943190,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:09:39.000Z","msg":"你咪投訴呀 砌你老母生豬肉架"},{"pid":"fa04da713e9750436a184453dd5965bb8babee9e","tid":943190,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"393315f14469e755106fa767f03fb27255df2078","tid":943190,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:09:39.000Z","msg":"你咪投訴呀 砌你老母生豬肉架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"支那公安應該唔止砌人生豬肉咁簡單"},{"pid":"2110ffc0556dfabd931f17e8cfa78f493bd36337","tid":943190,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"所以女警好重要<br />\n香港的話通常係搵女警搜返女仔, 避免誘惑和誤會"},{"pid":"587cd37c9e95334d38ee1dab07cacfd2c0a4dc7e","tid":943190,"uid":14275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"393315f14469e755106fa767f03fb27255df2078","tid":943190,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T11:09:39.000Z","msg":"你咪投訴呀 砌你老母生豬肉架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:02:59.000Z","msg":"好彩我老母食齋"},{"pid":"7d80e3c84481dcc9c81dda32be74e0b49dd23114","tid":943190,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"「見光的都這樣了，沒見光的更不用說 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u67Uedh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu67Uedh.jpg&h=c0f9517d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}